      <hedline>
        <hl1>Promotion at Salomon</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Salomon Smith Barney promotes Jay Mandelbaum to vice chairman and chief executive of its worldwide brokerage business (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Salomon Smith Barney unit of Citigroup has promoted Jay Mandelbaum to vice chairman and chief executive of its worldwide brokerage business. Salomon Smith Barney plans to expand its network of branches outside the United States. Mr. Mandelbaum, 37, reports to Michael Carpenter, chairman and chief executive of Salomon Smith Barney.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
